  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The trial is conducted in Asia. The aim of the trial is to evaluate the effect of insulin
      detemir on blood glucose control in Taiwanese patients with type 2 diabetes failing on OAD
      with/without once-daily NPH Insulin treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
